videos.description: Osharmar Abercrombie breaks fee for a 55-yard run to put Coast Carolina at Arkansas State's 20-yard line.
videos.headline: Abercrombie runs for 55 yards on first play

videos.description: Justice Hansen pass finds Chris Murray for a 12-yard touchdown pass to put Arkansas State ahead early in the game.
videos.headline: Arkansas State gets on the board first

videos.description: Dalton Demos punches in a 1-yard touchdown to even the score at 7-7.
videos.headline: Coastal Carolina evens score with TD run

videos.description: Justice Hansen completes a 10-yard touchdown pass to Blake Mack to give Arkansas State a 14-7 lead.
videos.headline: Hansen throws second TD pass

videos.description: Justice Hansen hooks up with Dijon Paschal on the outside for a 17-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Paschal beats defender and gets into the end zone

videos.description: Evan Rabon breaks free for a 55-yard punt return to Coast Carolina's 25-yard line.
videos.headline: Rabon bursts for a 55-yard punt return

videos.description: Justice Hansen throws a 4-yard touchdown pass to Kendrick Edwards to stretch Arkansas State's lead to 34-7.
videos.headline: Hansen hooks up with 4th receiver for TD

videos.description: Chris Jones reels in a pass from Kilton Anderson and stays on his feet for a 51-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jones shows great concentration on TD catch

videos.description: Justice Hansen finds a wide open Blake Mack for a 23-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Hansen and Mack connect for 2nd TD

videos.description: Kilton Anderson loses the football and Darreon Jackson scoops it up for a 28-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Arkansas State puts exclamation point on homecoming game with defensive score
